jagadguru adi shankara is a 2013 ensemble cast telugu biographical-devotional film produced by nara jaya sri devi on global peace creators banner , directed by j. k. bharavi . the film is based on the life of 8th century philosopher adi shankara . it stars kaushik babu in the lead role of adi shankaracharya , nagarjuna akkineni in a special appearance , mohan babu , srihari , and sai kumar in other important roles , and features music composed by nag sri vatsa .